settings.question: DO I HAVE TO REGISTER
settings.answer: Yes , we have retail products and in order to protect our salons we do not sell to general public.

settings.question: CAN VITAMIN LASH BOTOX BE USED WITH ANY BRAND?
settings.answer: Yes , apply it after tinting . It can be used as a stand-alone treatment as well for anyone who wants healthier, longer, fuller and thicker lashes.

settings.question: DO I HAVE TO TRAIN WITH MY LAMINATION IN ORDER TO USE THE PRODUCTS?
settings.answer: If you have already been trained in Lash Lift or Brow lamination ,you do not need to re train. swapping brands is easy with our protocols which are sent out with every order.

settings.question: DO YOU HAVE RETAIL PRODUCTS
settings.answer: Yes we have Vitamin Lash home care serum and Inspiration for retail.

settings.question: WHAT IS VITAMIN LASH BOTOX
settings.answer: Vitamin Lash Botox is  product which instantly nourishes the hair and gives it health, thickness but keeps on working to promote length and fulness long term too.  Vitamin Lash Botox is part of our lamination protocol and it will instantly thicken every single lash .

settings.question: I NEVER USED MY LAMINATION WILL I KNOW HOW LONG I NEED TO PROCESS THE SOLUTIONS FOR ?
settings.answer: We send out Lash lifting and Brow Lamination protocols with every order.
